+ *
+ * I changed all the .align's to 4 (16 byte alignment), as that's faster
+ * on a 486.
+ *
+ * Stack layout in 'ret_from_system_call':
+ * 	ptrace needs to have all regs on the stack.
+ *	if the order here is changed, it needs to be
